FAMHX.long_name: Fidelity Advisor Municipal Income 2025 Fund Class A
FAMHX.manager_bio: Since joining Fidelity Investments in 1997, Ms. McLaughlin has worked as an analyst and portfolio manager.
FAMHX.summary: The investment seeks as high a level of current income, exempt from federal income tax, as is consistent with the preservation of capital.  The fund normally invests at least 80% of assets in investment-grade municipal securities whose interest is exempt from federal income tax (but may be subject to the federal alternative minimum tax).

FCHPX.summary:
The investment seeks as high a level of current income, exempt from federal income tax, as is consistent with the preservation of capital.
